overview: Real life comes to the big screen and is expressed through a close-knit group of 5 friends who begin to experience the rollercoaster that life becomes in their 20s. They try to navigate everything from crescendos of happiness to unexpected turmoil that makes them tackle issues such as purpose, identity, relationships with family, friends, and of course...love.

title: Twenty Somethings
